{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How you got up?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At work?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where you took your lunch?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember a, a day, the routine of a day?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yes, well, we-- in Arlo, where, where, you know, where this, this timber work was done by us, we lived in a-- in a-- in a peasant house, which, at the back of it was a-- it would have been-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what do you call it in English, where the animals live?",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where the animals sleep, particularly-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a barn, let's call it a barn, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived, lived, lived in this barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a, a, a clay floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We put-- we put straw on that, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we made this comfortable as we could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in this barn, I remember, we, we had-- we, we would have had-- the particular barn I was, because there was a group of them-- it would have been, I imagine, 15 people that there was.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember a little other entrance to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it would be about 30 people in one barn, very narrow place allotted to each person.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And being in the country, it was no, no, no electric light there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very primitive, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- but it was summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was daylight fairly long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we went to bed very early.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think we had to be in bed by 8:00, 8:00 or 8:30, certainly by 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was no-- you know, it's really strange, Danny, when you are in these circumstances, your intellectual requirement is, is, is, is diminished to, to zero.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was-- to my recollection, it was very, very little in this way.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
